srallah on screen" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Article</div><div class="teaser-topic">Terrorism</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">Hezbollah&#039;s Record on War &amp; Politics</span></div><div class="teaser-byline"><div class="teaser-byline-text"><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">October 25, 2023</span></div></div></div></a><a class="teaser" data-type="article" href="/article/hamas-israel-war-views-wilson-center-experts"><div class="teaser-image"><picture><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_2372300809.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_2372300809.jpg" width="250" height="160" alt="Map of Israel and Vicinity Showing Gaza Strip under a magnifying glass" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Article</div><div class="teaser-topic">Security and Defense</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">Hamas-Israel War: Views From Wilson Center Experts</span></div><div class="teaser-byline"><div class="teaser-byline-text"><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">By&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-author">Robert Daly</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">October 24, 2023</span></div></div></div></a><a class="teaser" data-type="article" href="/article/doctrine-hamas"><div class="teaser-image"><picture><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_1548899321%20-%20web%20q_0.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_1548899321%20-%20web%20q_0.jpg" width="250" height="160" alt="Ismail Haniyeh" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-con